{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GJqJimgA4aHGfaWCAdtkLg","type":"tool_result","content":"### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Reviewer comparison done (Tier 3 #10). Remaining Tier 3: feed page (#11), share links (#12), sort & pagination (#13)\n- **pezantTools**: Only tailwindcss 3→4 remains as a pending major dep upgrade\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 35\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Social timeline feed page (Tier 3 #11) (PR #36, auto-merged)**\n- New `GET /api/feed` endpoint with:\n  - Cursor-based pagination (20 per page)\n  - Category filter via `?category=slug`\n  - Bulk reaction counts (helpful/agree) per review — no N+1 queries\n  - User's own reaction state per review\n  - Suggested reviewers (non-followed, with categories and review counts) for discovery\n- Rewrote CirclePage from flat list into social timeline:\n  - Day separators (\"Today\", \"Yesterday\", weekday names, full dates)\n  - Relative timestamps (\"2h ago\", \"3d ago\") on each card\n  - FeedCard component with reviewer avatar header, category badge, inline reactions using pre-fetched data\n  - Category filter pills (horizontal scroll)\n  - \"Load more\" cursor pagination button\n  - SuggestedReviewerCard for empty/small circles\n  - Two empty states: no follows (browse people CTA) and no reviews (suggested reviewers grid)\n  - \"People you might like\" section below feed when circle is small\n- 7 new tests: empty feed, suggested reviewers, reaction data in feed, user reaction state, category filtering, cursor pagination, suggestion exclusion of followed reviewers\n- 114 total tests (was 107), all passing, TypeScript clean, build verified\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Feed page done (Tier 3 #11). Remaining Tier 3: share links (#12), sort & pagination (#13)\n- **pezantTools**: Only tailwindcss 3→4 remains as a pending major dep upgrade\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 36\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Sort & pagination (Tier 3 #13) (PR #37-#39, auto-merged)**\n- Server-side sort support on 3 API endpoints:\n  - `GET /api/reviewers?sort=name|reviews|newest` — sort people by name (default), review count, or newest\n  - `GET /api/categories/:slug/reviews?sort=newest|rating_high|rating_low&page=N` — sort + offset pagination (20/page)\n  - `GET /api/reviewers/:handle?sort=newest|rating_high|rating_low` — sort reviewer's reviews\n- Reusable `SortPills` component for pill-style sort UI (ink/sand active state)\n- PeoplePage: sort pills (Name A–Z, Most reviews, Newest) alongside search filter\n- CategoryPage: sort pills in \"All reviews\" section + prev/next page navigation\n- PersonPage: sort pills below category filter for review ordering\n- 10 new tests: 3 for reviewer sort, 4 for category review sort + pagination, 3 for reviewer profile sort\n- 124 total tests (was 114), all passing, TypeScript clean, build verified\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Sort & pagination done (Tier 3 #13). Remaining Tier 3: share links (#12)\n- **pezantTools**: Only tailwindcss 3→4 remains as a pending major dep upgrade\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 37\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Share links (Tier 3 #12) (PR #41, auto-merged)**\n- `ShareButton` component with clipboard copy + Web Share API (native share sheet on mobile), pill-shaped design with \"Copied!\" feedback\n- Share button added to 4 pages: ReviewDetailPage, PersonPage, CategoryPage, ComparePage\n- Server-side OG meta tags middleware (`og-tags.ts`):\n  - Detects social media bot user-agents (Facebook, Twitter, Discord, Slack, LinkedIn, Telegram, WhatsApp, Google, Bing)\n  - Serves dynamic `og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image`, `og:url`, and Twitter Card meta tags\n  - Supports 4 entity types: reviews, reviewer profiles, categories, comparisons\n  - Handles base path stripping for production deployment\n  - Fallback default OG tags for unknown/home paths\n- 12 new tests: 8 for `getOgMeta` (all entity types, unknown entities, base path stripping, unmatched paths) + 4 for `renderOgHtml` (tag rendering, image inclusion/omission, HTML entity escaping)\n- 136 total tests (was 124), all passing, TypeScript clean, build verified\n\n### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: All Tier 3 features now complete (#9-#13). All Tiers 1-3 complete.\n- **pezantTools**: Only tailwindcss 3→4 remains as a pending major dep upgrade\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e791b648-3840-4faa-af8f-ce9ab800da29","uuid":"4a80f3d3-743d-4911-9903-0c426bbeef92","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:10:47.655Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"### Survey findings (for future sessions)\n- **trustedCircle**: Reviewer comparison done (Tier 3 #10). Remaining Tier 3: feed page (#11), share links (#12), sort & pagination (#13)\n- **pezantTools**: Only tailwindcss 3→4 remains as a pending major dep upgrade\n- **All repos**: Clean audit (except known unfixable transitive deps), tests passing, CI active, branches clean\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-20 — Run 35\n\n### What was done\n\n**trustedCircle — Social timeline feed page (Tier 3 #11) (PR #36, auto-merged)**\n- New `GET /api/feed` endpoint with:\n  - Cursor-based pagination (20 per page)\n  - Category filter via `?category=slug`\n  - Bulk reaction counts (helpful/agree) per review — no N+1 queries\n  - User's own reaction state per review\n  - Suggested reviewers (non-followed, with categories and review counts) for discovery\n- Rewrot